body_html:
I also have faced with this problem. Inference time after 8-bit quantisation is 2x times slower for my iOS app.

Also after quantisation the quality of my regression model became much worse. Perhaps this is not related to this issue. Obviously, quantisation should affect on quality. But didn't expect such degradation.
